(U.S.); UNITED STATES -- ARMS SALES -- IRAN; MILITARY EQUIPMENT AND SUPPLIES; 
CHEMICALS; ROCKET FUEL; PRODUCT BANS; IRAN -- DEFENSE; IMPOUNDMENT; GIRINDUS 
CORP; BUREAUCRACY 
