floor of Phelps Hall and 20 to 40 students awaiting rescue on a third-floor 
ledge, Collum said. "Firefighters evacuated all the students from the building 
safely," he said, and the blaze was controlled in 35 minutes. The cost of the 
damage was estimated at $30,000. 
